  "Subtitles": {
    "Entries": [
      {
        "Region": 3,
        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 440,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8650,
            "LocalizeKR": "후후. 어떠신가요.\n밀레니엄 최고 미소녀의\n맨발을 씻겨줄 기회라니…",
            "LocalizeJP": "ふふっ、どうでしょう？\nミレニアム最高の美少女の足を\n洗う機会なんて…。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 450,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9250,
            "LocalizeKR": "좀처럼 흔치 않은…\n흔치 않은 기회의…",
            "LocalizeJP": "なかなかお目にかかれ…\nかかれないはずの…。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 460,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11000,
            "LocalizeKR": "읏…?\n생각했던 것보다…\n뭔가 이상한 듯한…",
            "LocalizeJP": "っ…？\n思ったより…\nなんだか変な…",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 470,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9100,
            "LocalizeKR": "기묘한 게…\n부, 부끄럽다고 할지…\n어, 어째서…?",
            "LocalizeJP": "奇妙な…\nは、恥ずかしいというか…\nど、どうして…？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 480,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7700,
            "LocalizeKR": "마, 말로 표현하기\n어려운 감정이…!",
            "LocalizeJP": "げ、言語化が難しい感情が…！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 490,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12000,
            "LocalizeKR": "단순히 선생님이 제 발을\n정성스럽게 씻겨주고\n있을 뿐일 텐데…\n어째서…?",
            "LocalizeJP": "ただ、先生が私の足を\n丁寧に洗ってくださっている\nだけだというのに…\nどうして…？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 500,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12200,
            "LocalizeKR": "후, 후훗. 네, 물론\n각오는 되어 있으니\n신경 쓰지 마시길.\n부디, 마음가는대로…!",
            "LocalizeJP": "ふ、ふふっ。ええ、\nもちろん覚悟はできて\nおりますので、お気になさらず。\nどうぞ、心ゆくまで…！",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 510,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11300,
            "LocalizeKR": "…각오는, 되어 있을…\n테니, 까요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "…覚悟は、できている…\nはず、ですので。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 20020,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 2002001,
            "DisplayOrder": 520,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 6,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13000,
            "LocalizeKR": "네, 네에. 그, 그럼…\n잘 부탁드립니다…",
            "LocalizeJP": "え、ええ…で、では…\nよろしくお願いします…。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle6",
